subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: The Wimbledon draw, which resembles a game of bingo with its grids and numbers drawn from a basket, has prescribed some interesting matchups, including a possible Justine Henin-Serena Williams quarterfinal.
